  <official_title>A Phase 2B, Multi-Center, Randomized, Double-Blinded, Parallel-Arm , Study to Assess Efficacy and Safety of 3'-Aminomethylnicotine-P. Aeruginosa r-Exoprotein A Conjugate Vaccine (NicVAX速) or Placebo Co-Administered With Varenicline (Champix速) as an Aid in Smoking Cessation</official_title>
