  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of NicVAX co-administered
      with varenicline as an aid in smoking cessation over a one-year period in smokers who want to
      quit smoking.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
